---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about me and my journey"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Hi! I'm a passionate developer and writer who loves exploring new technologies and sharing my experiences through this blog.
	</p>

	<p>
		My journey in tech started several years ago, and since then I've had the opportunity to work on various exciting projects. 
		From web development to exploring emerging technologies, I'm always eager to learn and grow.
	</p>

	<p>
		Through this blog, I share my thoughts on programming, technology trends, and lessons learned from my experiences. 
		Whether it's a deep dive into a technical topic or reflections on the tech industry, I aim to provide valuable insights 
		that can help fellow developers and tech enthusiasts.
	</p>

	<p>
		When I'm not coding or writing, you can find me exploring new places, reading books, or contributing to open-source projects. 
		I believe in the power of community and continuous learning, and I'm always open to connecting with like-minded individuals.
	</p>

	<p>
		Feel free to reach out if you'd like to discuss technology, collaborate on projects, or just have a chat. 
		Thanks for visiting my blog, and I hope you find the content helpful and inspiring!
	</p>
</Layout>
